divs: Sighting DetailsI was outside taking pictures of clouds and chemtrails. It wasn't until after I took all the pictures that I was looking through them on my digital camera is when I saw something that I couldn't see with my naked eye. This is the second time I have caught something unexplainable on a picture I have taken in the past 2 years. I'm not sure if it is anything military or extraterristreal. In the picture you need to look up in the left side corner an zoom in to see what it is. In the second picture that I have uploaded is actually the the picture I took before I took the picture that captured the black object.
